      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To establish a short-term moratorium on the payment of principal or interest on certain mortgage loans secured by residential or commercial real estate located in any area declared to be a Federal disaster area due to Hurricane Katrina or Hurricane Rita, and for other purposes.</title>
